flowchart TD
    Start([User Query]) --> Process[process_query]
    Process --> GetContext[Get Context from ContextManager]
    GetContext --> RAG[Generate RAG Response]
    RAG --> CheckLayers{Detected Layers?}
    
    CheckLayers -->|Yes| GenActions[Generate Map Actions<br/>for each layer]
    CheckLayers -->|No| EmptyActions[Empty Actions List]
    
    GenActions --> UpdateContext[Update Context Manager]
    EmptyActions --> UpdateContext
    
    UpdateContext --> Return[Return ChatResponse]
    Return --> End([Response to User])
    
    style Process fill:#1a4d5c,stroke:#2d7a8f,color:#fff
    style RAG fill:#5c4d1a,stroke:#
